# mbuf_leadingspace

**Function**

## Declaration

```swift
size_t mbuf_leadingspace(const mbuf_t mbuf);
```

## Parameters

- **mbuf**: The mbuf.

## Return Value

The number of unused bytes at the start of the mbuf.

## Discussion

Determines the space available in the mbuf proceeding the current data.
